data.description: Amazing home in the heart of McAllen. This cozy home is sitting in the peaceful Green Valley Estates close to Dove and 2nd Rd. Walk in to the open living and dining spaces with is tall ceilings which increase the feeling of amplitude. Patio was enclosed with A/C to add a living area where you can entertain friends and family and the mature trees in the backyard will give shade all year long to enjoy your gatherings. Do not miss out on this opportunity!
